Package io.atlasmap.spi

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionProcessor
    The field action processor.
    AtlasCollectionHelper
    The interface for the collection helper class.
    AtlasCombineStrategy Deprecated.
    COMBINE/SEPARATE mode has been deprecated.
    AtlasConversionService
    The AtlasMap conversion service resolves the appropriate AtlasConverter to convert the field value and apply.
    AtlasConverter<T>
    The converter interface.
    AtlasFieldAction
    The field action interface.
    AtlasFieldActionService
    AtlasFieldActionService handles AtlasMap field action.
    AtlasFieldReader
    AtlasFieldReader reads the field value from source document.
    AtlasFieldWriter
    AtlasFieldWriter writes the field value to the target document.
    AtlasInternalSession
    The internal version of AtlasSession which provides extended access to the internal AtlasMap components.
    AtlasInternalSession.Head
    The AtlasInternalSession.Head object represents what is under processing right now.
    AtlasModule
    A SPI contract between AtlasMap core and modules.
    AtlasModuleInfo
    Represents AtlasModule metadata.
    AtlasModuleInfoRegistry
    The runtime registry of AtlasModuleInfo.
    AtlasPropertyStrategy
    A plug-in interface for property strategy which read a source property and write a target property.
    AtlasSeparateStrategy Deprecated.
    COMBINE/SEPARATE mode has been deprecated.
    AtlasValidator
    The interface for validator implementations.
    FunctionFactory
    The factory class to create function expression.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AtlasConversionConcern
    The enumeration of conversion concerns which represents the concerns about the data conversion.
    AtlasModuleMode
    The enumeration of the AtlasModule mode, specifically AtlasModuleMode.SOURCE for the source document, AtlasModuleMode.TARGET for the target document, and AtlasModuleMode.UNSET for none of those.
    AtlasPropertyType
    The type of the property.
    FieldDirection
    The enumeration of the field direction, whether it's source or target.
    StringDelimiter
    The enumeration of the string delimters.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AtlasActionProcessor
    The annotation to add on a field action method.
    AtlasConversionInfo
    The annotation to be set on the converter method.
    AtlasFieldActionInfo Deprecated.
    Use AtlasActionProcessor instead
    AtlasModuleDetail
    AtlasModuleDetail adds metadata onto AtlasModule.
